title: What Makes 'Invincible' Stand Out
description:
Charles Holmes and Jomi Adeniran discuss the newest creation from Robert Kirkman, 'Invincible,' that is now streaming on Amazon Prime. They break down what makes this superhero show notable and worth watching.
Hosts: Charles Holmes and Jomi Adeniran
